  • Classes in com.structed.dal used by com.structed.dal 
    Class and Description
    Reader
    An interface for reader type The interface contains two functions: 1) read the data as an two dimensional array of strings 2) read the data as an Instance Container (one of the package data structure)
    StandardReader
    A standard reader It reads the data in the following format: label index_of_feature_i:value_of_feature_i (this holds also for sparse data, when many values are zeros, see mnist data for example)
    Writer
    An interface for writing the data/models
